# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Unreleased]

## [0.6.0] - 2021-01-11

### Fixed
- Disabled HTTPS cert check that sometimes prevents model download (#105)
- Removed non-fasttext code and dependencies (#96)

## [0.5.0] - 2020-02-28
### Added
- fastText-based toxic comment model implementation (#53)
- Global main module for dostoevsky package, that can be called as python -m dostoevsky

### Fixed
- As global main module is available, windows users can call it for models download procedure (#52)
